      "text": "# Leaving with preparation and farewell\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "e9d9a3d3081bd4ad",
      "text": "The first station, namely the starting point of the fetching, is here. It is the place where I am; and it is the place where I leave. Accordingly, my activities are divided into stationary and ambulatory. Still lingering here, I prepare myself, but also others and others, for the fact that I am about to fetch something here; and then I set out, go off to really do it. "
